<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I am struggling to finish. But I only have 100 pages to go and am determined to get it done. If I had any more pages to read then I would probably put<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I am struggling to finish. But I only have 100 pages to go and am determined to get it done. If I had any more pages to read then I would probably put it down and not bother with it. It is a bit like someone telling me their life story - very mundane and not engaging.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
