        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer32714119" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16311557257927487709">This thinly veiled fictional account of Laura Bush was absolutely fantastic. I&apos;m sure the First Lady will be embarrassed by certain juicy, fabricated events, but all in all, I found this to be a love letter to her from the author, who claims to be a huge Laura Bush groupie. Sittenfeld is a true master of character development and this is some of the best fiction I&apos;ve read in awhile--I couldn&apos;t put it down and stayed up way too late reading it.</span>
