<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/56473085-heartsick"><img alt="Heartsick: Three stories about love and loss, and what happens in between" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1618358089l/56473085._SX98_.jpg" />
